WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.400
The course is like a big diamond.

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:06.460
So we have to make turns around each buoy.

00:00:06.460 --> 00:00:09.480
So we can turn quickly to another buoy,

00:00:09.480 --> 00:00:12.000
and make another quick turn,

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:15.080
and make sure that we head back to the finish.

00:00:15.080 --> 00:00:19.100
We are basically racing the clock, not other people.

